<inglise> REGULATION (EEC) No 2364/75 OF THE COMMISSION of 15 September 1975 on the calculation of aids in the form of loans at reduced rates of interest or of interest rebates which are not specified in percentage points </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 2364/75, mis k&auml;sitleb toetuste arvutamist, mida antakse v&auml;hendatud intressim&auml;&auml;raga laenudena v&otilde;i protsentides v&auml;ljendamata intressitoetustena 15. september 1975 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 724/75 (1) of 18 March 1975 establishing a European Regional Fund, and in particular Article 4 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 18. m&auml;rtsi 1975. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 724/75, millega asutatakse Euroopa Regionaalarengu Fond, (1) ja eriti selle artiklit 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the application of this Regulation requires that State aids in the form of loans at reduced interest rates or of interest rebates which are not specified in percentage points should be capable of being compared and added up; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse rakendamine eeldab, et v&auml;hendatud intressim&auml;&auml;raga laenudena v&otilde;i protsentides v&auml;ljendamata intressitoetustena antavad riiklikud toetused oleksid v&otilde;rreldavad ja liidetavad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas this calculation should be made by reference to the interest rate used for comparable operations which is in force at the time of the granting of the reduced interest loan or interest rebate; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealusel arvutamisel tuleks arvesse v&otilde;tta v&otilde;rreldavate tehingute puhul kasutatavat intressim&auml;&auml;ra, mis kehtib v&auml;hendatud intressim&auml;&auml;raga laenu v&otilde;i intressitoetuse andmisel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas such forms of aid are only provided in certain Member States; whereas there is therefore no need to specify reference rates for the other Member States; </inglise>
<eesti> sellises vormis abi antakse &uuml;ksnes teatavates liikmesriikides; seet&otilde;ttu on vaja teistele liikmesriikidele kehtestada viitem&auml;&auml;rad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Fund Committee, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las fondikomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> In all cases where a loan is granted at a reduced rate of interest or where an interest rebate is not stated in advance to be a rebate of a specific number of percentage points, the amount of the reduction in the interest rate or of the rebate shall be calculated on the basis of a reference rate. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui laenu antakse v&auml;hendatud intressim&auml;&auml;raga v&otilde;i intressitoetus ei ole eelnevalt protsentides kindlaks m&auml;&auml;ratud, arvutatakse intressim&auml;&auml;ra v&auml;henduse v&otilde;i intressitoetuse suurus viitem&auml;&auml;ra p&otilde;hjal. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The reference rates for the Member States mentioned below shall be as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> J&auml;rgmiste liikmesriikide viitem&auml;&auml;rad on j&auml;rgmised: </eesti>
<inglise> Belgium: rate for loans of 10 years and over granted by the Soci&eacute;t&eacute; Nationale de Cr&eacute;dit &aacute; l'Industrie; </inglise>
<eesti> Belgia: Soci&eacute;t&eacute; Nationale de Cr&eacute;dit &agrave; l'Industrie antavate v&auml;hemalt 10aastaste laenude intressim&auml;&auml;r; </eesti>
<inglise> Denmark: rate for loans granted by the European Investment Bank increased by 1.5 percentage points; </inglise>
<eesti> Taani: Euroopa Investeerimispanga antavate laenude intressim&auml;&auml;r pluss 1,5 protsenti; </eesti>
<inglise> France: rate for loans for plant and machinery granted by the Cr&eacute;dit National; </inglise>
<eesti> Prantsusmaa: nende laenude intressim&auml;&auml;r, mida Cr&eacute;dit National annab masinate ja seadmete hankimiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Italy: reference rate fixed by the State for the payment of interest rebates to credit institutions; </inglise>
<eesti> Itaalia: viitem&auml;&auml;r, mille riik on kehtestanud intressitoetuste maksmiseks krediidiasutustele; </eesti>
<inglise> Federal Republic of Germany: rate for 10-year loans (programme M I and M II) granted by the Kreditanstalt f&uuml;r Wiederaufbau; </inglise>
<eesti> Saksamaa Liitvabariik: Kreditanstalt f&uuml;r Wiederaufbau antavate 10aastaste laenude (programmid M I ja M II) intressim&auml;&auml;r; </eesti>
<inglise> United Kingdom: rate of interest known as the "broad commercial rate". </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;hendkuningriik: intressim&auml;&auml;r, mida tuntakse nime all "broad commercial rate". </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> In each case the reference rate in force on the day of the decision to grant the interest rebate or the reduced interest loan shall be used. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga kord kasutatakse viitem&auml;&auml;ra, mis kehtib p&auml;eval, mil tehakse otsus anda intressitoetust v&otilde;i v&auml;hendatud intressim&auml;&auml;raga laenu. </eesti>
<inglise> This rate shall be indicated in the request for assistance from the Fund. </inglise>
<eesti> See m&auml;&auml;r m&auml;rgitakse Euroopa Regionaalarengu Fondile esitatavale abitaotlusele. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the fifth day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub viiendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 15 September 1975. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 15. september 1975 </eesti>
